name: reborne.fun
description: Instead of launching new tokens, it lets users adopt existing failed tokens and bring them back to life. You can CTO (Call-To-Own) a token, take ownership, and build a community around it. The platform also tracks who revives the most, how much SOL is spent, and ranks top revivers—rewarding them with real incentives. It’s not about adding more noise to the space. It’s about cleaning it up and giving forgotten tokens a second chance, powered by transparent mechanics, live trading data, and a growing ecosystem of degens who know how to spot hidden value.
